product_name: Paris Corner 100ml Ministry of Oud - Oud Satin EDP Unisex Spray Pendora Scents Fragrance Long-Lasting Perfume PERFUMES
product_features:
Oud Satin is a Oriental Woody fragrance for women and men. The fragrance features agarwood (oud), bulgarian rose, benzoin, turkish rose, violet and vanilla.
A rich resinous powdery fragrance with soft rose and oud.
The vanilla and rose notes flutter in and out of the spotlight but the focus is always on the oud.
Oud Satin starts out strong but then creates a soft, hazy aura around the wearer.
The perfume is unisex, beautifully blended, has moderate to strong projection and excellent longevity.

product_name: 18.21 Man Made Men’s Cologne, Sweet Tobacco Fragrance, 3.4 Fl. Oz - Long-Lasting Eau De Parfum for Men, Sweet Scent with Woodsy Undertones - Eau De Toilette with Masculine Aromatics
product_features:
A MASCULINE AROMA: Our signature oil blend will leave a lasting impression with classic aromatics. Citrus, spicy saffron, and dried fruits reveal hints of tonka bean, honey, and vanilla that sweeten undertones of tobacco, exotic woods and musk.
VINTAGE BOTTLE FOR THE MODERN MAN: Inspired by the roaring spirit of swanky, Prohibition-era speakeasies, our cologne (a true Eau de Parfum)  comes furnished in an elegant glass bottle that sports a fine-mist atomizer. It creates a sleek, polished aesthetic that won’t leak.
ALL-DAY FRAGRANCE: With a rich, complex mixture of nearly 30 oils, our cologne has a 10-12-hour projection and a sillage that will linger in the air. Apply 1-2 mists from the atomizer directly to skin near pulse points. A little goes a long way.
PREMIUM QUALITY OIL BLEND: This is a parfum-grade scent that is made in small batches in a niche barrel house. It contains a 20% oil blend, 80% denatured alcohol, and no water, for a sweet, unmistakable depth of fragrance that transcends gender.
LUXURY GIFT SET: Our superior and exclusive tobacco vanilla colognes make great gifts for your dad, husband, or grandfather. This strong, smooth, aromatic perfume will impress that special man in your life on his birthday, Father’s Day, or Christmas.

Tropical and Beachy Perfume: Sail away to your perfect island escape with every spritz of this delicious summer-inspired fragrance.

product_name: IT'S TIME By Bruce Buffer Eau de Parfum For Men 3.4 fl. oz
product_features:
Bruce Buffer has introduced the world’s greatest champions in his illustrious career as the LEGENDARY VOICE OF MIXED MARTIAL ARTS, and now IT’S TIME for him to introduce you to his signature fragrance.
What’s the difference between an Eau de Parfum (EdP) and a Cologne? Unlike its counterparts, Eau de Toilette and Cologne, EdP is formulated with a higher concentration of fragrance oils, making it last longer and smell stronger - the perfect choice for long days or special occasions.
EdP is also more complex than a Cologne. The higher concentration of fragrance oils allows the IT’s TIME By Bruce Buffer EdP to be made up of a combination of different scents, including top, middle, and base notes. This creates a unique, layered scent that evolves as the fragrance dries down, providing a long-lasting and sophisticated experience.

Dareej for men is a spicy, flirty and romantic concoction that opens on strong spicy notes and meanders through the floral middle notes laced with a whiff of romance by the rose highlights. Daarej for Women to a sweet earthy lingering creaminess by sandalwood, vanilla and caramel. Daarej Pour Femme is deeply romantic and a dreamer. ABOUT LA YUQAWAM FOR MEN: The series extends a classic yet modern feel full of elegance, refinement and prestige to oriental perfumery. The love for this series transcends beyond the originally targeted Arab nationalities to international connoisseurs of perfumes, looking for a sophisticated and modern exhilarating oriental experience. La Yuqawam Pour Homme swells with sensuality, this fragrance is a refined adornment for a man who is desirable, powerful, refined and elegant.

MIDDLE NOTES: Jasmine, artemisia and olibanum
BASE NOTES: Leather, suede, amber and woody notes.

product_name: RASASI Hawas EDP 100ml(3.4 oz) | Long-Lasting Pour Homme Spray, Aquatic Scent Designed to Embody Masculine Strength and Vigor (Hawas for Him)
product_features:
About Hawas - Hawas for Him blends cinnamon, bergamot, orange blossom, grey amber and sandalwood to create an aquatic scent designed to embody masculine strength and vigor. This fresh elegant woody perfume combines the premium Italian citrus and the fruity freshness of pear and pineapple. The heart of this modern fougere is based on aquatic elements combined with melon and violet.
About Daarej - Dareej for men is a spicy, flirty and romantic concoction that opens on strong spicy notes and meanders through the floral middle notes laced with a whiff of romance by the rose highlights. The base notes are a delightful mélange of earthy, soft, creamy and lingering notes of sandalwood, tempered to sweet warmth by amber and Tonka beans. The intoxicating and seductive notes of animalistic musk are caressed by plumes of dark and smoky exotic patchouli.
About Shuhrah - Shuhrah for men blends bergamot, frankincense, cedar wood, oak moss & Oudh with floral inflecti Hawas for Her incorporates pomegranate, jasmine sambac and vetiver for an haute couture perfume aimed at women who are seeking an edgy, yet chic fashion statement. Top Notes: Apple, Grapefruit, & Pomegranate Middle Notes: Jasmine Sambac, Iris Natural, & Citrus Base Notes: Patchouli, Vetiver, & Praline.
Hawas for Her incorporates pomegranate, jasmine sambac and vetiver for an haute couture perfume aimed at women who are seeking an edgy, yet chic fashion statement. Top Notes: Apple, Grapefruit, & Pomegranate Middle Notes: Jasmine Sambac, Iris Natural, & Citrus Base Notes: Patchouli, Vetiver, & Praline.
Daarej Pour Femme is a fruity floral fragrance with a unique green accord in the opening notes. The floral bouquet of middle notes adds a softness and romance to the perfume. Top Notes: Bergamot, Orange, Green, Accord, & Peach Middle Notes: Muguet, Jasmine, Tuberose, Orchid, & Heliotrope Base Notes: Vanilla, Carmel, Vetiver, Patchouli, Sandal, Amber & Musk.
Shuhrah for women blends notes of rose, freesia, bergamot, lily of valley, grey amber and musk to create a perfume that is simply a floral ode to feminine elegance. This everyday fresh perfume befits a woman who is an effortless charmer. Top Note: Lemon & Sage Middle Note: Iris, Jasmine, & Lily of the Valley Base Note: Oud, Pathouli, Grey Amber, & Musk.

The opulence and enigmatic mystique of oriental olfactory find contemporary expression in four unique scent journeys that are addictive & accentuated by distinctive features. These perfumes celebrate the love for bling as a language of self-expression and revel in easy elegance and an irresistibly infectious joie de vivre. Ebhar is a sublime fragrance with a unique contrast
TOP NOTES: Sparkling Lemon, Green Apple
MIDDLE NOTES: Lotus Flower, Orris, Pure Jasmine, Damask Rose
BASE NOTES: Intense Vanilla, Addictive Praline, Tonka Beans, Musk

product_name: RASASI Shuhrah for Men EDP-90 ML(3.0 oz)|- Exotic Oriental I Sandal,Cedar,Jasmine,Amber,Oudh,Leathery, Rose, & Tomato Leaves
product_features:
ABOUT: In Arabic, Shuhrah refers to someone who is famous or has a strongly established reputation. Rasasi Shuhrah cologne is designed to power above all other fragrances; you will be noticed! A unique and explosive scent, there is no room for subtlety. The projection is devastating, the longevity monstrous and the sillage is explosive. This is an enigmatic cologne – entirely irreverent, addictive, a bit standoffish and intensely masculine, yet cheerful and uplifting.
TOP NOTES: Rose, Tomato Leaves, Freesia
MIDDLE NOTES: Rose, Sandalwood, Cedarwood, Jasmine
BASE NOTES: Amber, Musk, Oakmoss, Oudh, Leathery
BLEND: Shuhrah for men blends bergamot, frankincense, cedar wood, oak moss & Oudh with floral inflections to create a fresh woody masculine scent that is uplifting and charismatic.
ORIENTAL: The top opens with pure bloodlust: romantic red rose joins fresh green tomato leaves and radiant freesia flowers. In perfumery, the smell of tomato leaf is often used to signal freshness or to impart the feeling of the outdoors. This oriental fragrance contains exotic notes of jasmine.
EXOTIC: It leans toward the lighter side of sandalwood. It's an overall clean and fresh fragrance, making it a great option for everyday wear. This makes sense as this scent probably remind men of happy memories, positive emotions and an overlying feeling of comfort.

product_features:
PROTECTIVE SKIN-BARRIER SPRAY: SKIN-PREP Spray forms a film designed to protect intact skin. When applied, it forms a barrier that acts as a protective interface between the skin and bodily wastes, fluids, adhesive dressings, drainage tubes, and surrounding ostomy sites.
EASY TO APPLY & CARRY: This convenient spray makes it easy to travel with and to apply a topical barrier that helps protect skin from adhesive trauma or incontinence-related dermatitis. Use it on knees, heels, elbows, and other areas of the body that are at risk of irritation due to friction damage.
EFFECTIVE PROTECTION BETWEEN TAPE & SKIN: The barrier created by the spray helps prepare intact skin for attachment sites, tapes, films, and any adhesive dressings that you use on a daily basis. Removal of SKIN-PREP isn’t necessary before reapplication.
HOW TO USE: Wash the affected skin area, rinse, and allow to dry thoroughly. Hold the bottle approximately 8" from skin, spray lightly and allow to dry, then spray a second light coat. SKIN-PREP may be removed with soap and water. Do not spray on, or apply directly to, open wounds or mucous membranes.
OUR PROMISE: Smith & Nephew has pioneered health solutions since 1856 with one mission: to use technology to take the limits off living. Our bodies should never put our potential on hold, so this two-word promise inspires all that we do: Life Unlimited.
